Uses of Package
org.llrp.ltk.net

  • Packages that use org.llrp.ltk.net 
    Package Description
    org.llrp.ltk.net  
  • Classes in org.llrp.ltk.net used by org.llrp.ltk.net 
    Class and Description
    LLRPConnection
    LLRPConnection represents an abstract interface for an LLRP connection at a LLRP reader or client.
    LLRPConnectionAttemptFailedException
    LLRPConnectionAttemptFailedException is thrown whenever a connection with the reader could not be established
    LLRPEndpoint
    The LLRPEndpoint interface needs to be implemented by any class that wants to receive LLRP messages asynchronously.
    LLRPIoHandlerAdapter
    LLRPIoHandlerAdapter defines abstract methods that need to be implemented by any LLRPIoHandlerAdaptor implementation in addition to the methods defined by the Apache MINA IoHandler interface.
